│  billing, while others price by usage. 3. **Artifact support:** can your registry support any artifacts (Helm charts, OCI artifacts,  │
│  etc.) aside from Docker/container images? It can sometimes be helpful to consolidate here. 4. **Feature set:** many registries have  │
